66V174H959L915 212V393H845Z\" style=\"fill:var(--ink)\"></path><path d=\"M0 393L173 13H250L78 393H0Z\" style=\"fill:var(--accent)\"></path></svg><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"w-2 rounded-xs\" style=\"height:18px;background:var(--accent);animation:blink 1.15s steps(1) infinite\"></span></a><div class=\"hidden items-center gap-0.5 md:flex\"><a class=\"nav-link\" data-active=\"false\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"nav-link\" data-active=\"false\" href=\"/projects\">Projects</a><a class=\"nav-link\" data-active=\"false\" href=\"/articles\">Articles</a><a class=\"nav-link\" data-active=\"false\" href=\"/tours\">Tours</a><a class=\"nav-link\" data-active=\"false\" href=\"/about\">About</a></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><a aria-label=\"mkdir\" class=\"glass-pill mono h-10 shrink-0 gap-1.5 px-2.5 text-[13px] font-medium sm:px-3.5\" style=\"color:var(--ink)\" href=\"/mkdir\"><svg width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.9\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\"><polyline points=\"4 17 10 11 4 5\"></polyline><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"19\" x2=\"20\" y2=\"19\"></line></svg><span class=\"hidden sm:inline\"><span style=\"color:var(--accent-ink)\"></span>mkdir</span></a><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Switch to dark theme\" class=\"glass-icon-btn flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"md:hidden\"><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-nav-panel\" class=\"glass-icon-btn flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"18\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></nav></div></div><!--$--><!--$--><main class=\"relative z-[3] mx-auto w-full max-w-[820px] px-[22px] pt-28 pb-16 sm:pt-32\"><a class=\"mono inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[12.5px] transition-colors hover:text-(--accent-ink)\" style=\"color:var(--ink-dim)\" href=\"/articles\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"transform:rotate(180deg)\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg>All articles</a><div class=\"mt-5 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2.5\"><span class=\"badge\" style=\"color:var(--accent-ink);background:var(--chip);border-color:var(--chip-brd)\">Data</span><span class=\"chip mono px-2 py-1 text-[10.5px] font-medium\" style=\"border-radius:7px\">EN</span><span class=\"mono text-[12px]\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">Apr 2026<!-- --> · <!-- -->1 min read</span></div><h1 class=\"mt-3 font-bold\" style=\"font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,44px);line-height:1.12;letter-spacing:-0.03em\">Building a Data Science Portfolio Around Financial Distress Prediction</h1><p class=\"mt-4 text-[16px]\" style=\"line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-dim)\">A reflection on turning a thesis topic into a portfolio-ready data science project.</p><div class=\"mt-6 aspect-[16/9] w-full\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;border-radius:15px\"><img alt=\"Financial disstress illustration\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"https://cms.daffa.me/uploads/financialdistress_39c845d325.jpg\"/></div><article class=\"mt-8\"><p class=\"mt-4 text-[15.5px] first:mt-0\" style=\"line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink)\">My current main data science project focuses on financial distress prediction for Indonesian public companies. Instead of treating the thesis only as an academic requirement, I want to structure it as a portfolio project that clearly shows the full data science workflow: problem framing, data preparation, exploratory analysis, modeling, evaluation, and communication.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-[15.5px] first:mt-0\" style=\"line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink)\">The main challenge is not only building a model, but also explaining why the model matters. Financial distress prediction sits at the intersection of finance, business, and machine learning. This makes it useful for showing both technical and analytical thinking.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-[15.5px] first:mt-0\" style=\"line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink)\">For the portfolio version, I plan to present the project through notebooks, visualizations, model comparison tables, and a concise explanation of the business context.</p></article><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-[7px]\"><span class=\"chip mono px-[9px] py-1 text-[11px]\" style=\"border-radius:8px\">#<!-- -->data science</span><span class=\"chip mono px-[9px] py-1 text-[11px]\" style=\"border-radius:8px\">#<!-- -->machine learning</span><span class=\"chip mono px-[9px] py-1 text-[11px]\" style=\"border-radius:8px\">#<!-- -->financial distress</span><span class=\"chip mono px-[9px] py-1 text-[11px]\" style=\"border-radius:8px\">#<!-- -->portfolio</span><span class=\"chip mono px-[9px] py-1 text-[11px]\" style=\"border-radius:8px\">#<!-- -->thesis</span></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--><!--/$--><!--/$--><footer class=\"relative z-[3] flex justify-center px-[22px] pt-[30px] pb-11\"><div class=\"flex w-full max-w-[1180px] flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-[18px] sm:px-[22px]\" style=\"border-radius:20px;background:var(--glass-bg);background-image:var(--glass-tint);backdrop-filter:blur(var(--glass-blur)) saturate(180%);border:1px solid var(--glass-brd);box-shadow:inset 0 1px 0 var(--glass-hi)\"><span class=\"text-[13px]\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">© 2026 Daffa Ilham Restupratama</span><span class=\"mono text-[11px]\" style=\"color:var(--ink-faint)\">Data · Business · Finance · Maps · Walking Tours</span></div></footer></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0a1gboz92241g.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[81064,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2miu-xgxthh4m.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"ThemeProvider\\\"]\\n3:I[31108,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2miu-xgxthh4m.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"RouteProgress\\\"]\\n4:I[6809,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2miu-xgxthh4m.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"Nav\\\"]\\n5:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2miu-xgxthh4m.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2miu-xgxthh4m.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n7:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2miu-xgxthh4m.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"LoadingBoundaryProvider\\\"]\\nf:I[68027,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2miu-xgxthh4m.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\",1]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2vnee9rqmfix3.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/051742360c26797e-s.p.1bkzbscqrt8rl.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\",{\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"font/woff2\\\"}]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/83afe278b6a6bb3c-s.p.2bn3s6zvc0dyp.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\",{\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"font/woff2\\\"}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:{\\\"P\\\":null,\\\"c\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"articles\\\",\\\"building-data-science-portfolio-financial-distre